{"tid":2409586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（BNO）八 十 歲 婆 婆 BNO 移 民 英 國","createTime":"2021-02-16T02:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T09:57:18.000Z","uid":361751,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"955b8ad5f82c4a47aa729794b63acced336f59b0","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1qQgYw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1qQgYw.png&h=6085b795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/599116127417126/posts/731533987508672/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F599116127417126%2Fposts%2F731533987508672%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=09d1bcdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/599116127417126/posts/731533987508672/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n外婆要移民<br />\n<br />\n小時候係外公外婆湊大的，特別有感情，外公十幾年前不在了，外婆到現在都同我父母同住。過去半年講到移民，都會諗咁外婆點呢？外婆雖然差不多80歲，但身體幾好，好有中氣，仲可以過年整24底年糕。英國近幾年也去過好幾次，倫敦同愛丁堡都去過，因為有家人喺度住。<br />\n<br />\n外婆喜歡英國的花園，夏天時會種下花。不喜歡英國的食物，有得揀一定要食中餐。覺得洗碗機都係信唔過，堅持手洗。<br />\n<br />\n每年夏天黎英國一兩個月的外婆，到底可唔可以真係喺度住呢？無得日日飲茶又真係得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n我們呢個extended family 有傾過，最後結果係因為所有子女都會走，所以外婆好有機會會跟隨。但係，移民咁大件事，每個家庭成員都應該有say, 每個人既睇法同感受都係重要既。問外婆既話，佢係答「你走我就走」(you jump I jump啲friend)。<br />\n<br />\n答就係答咗，但我心裏面仲有啲不安，會諗好多，其實會唔會係我地走，佢根本無得揀？就好似有得揀只想食中餐？有得揀都會想子女都喺香港？<br />\n<br />\n但<span class=\"red\">人生有幾多時係真正有得揀？</span><br />\n<br />\n有時候都會諗太祖父母當年可以揀<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>留喺廣州，可以揀落香港</strong></span></span>，揀咗香港，又有咗一代一代，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">當年佢地落既決定，影響以後既好多人</span></strong></span>。外婆依家80歲，還可以跟著我們再走一走，其實可能都幾大意義。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日同外婆視訊拜年，佢話最近買咗對新波鞋，打算黎英國著😂 牀下底啲舊衫都唔要啦，帶啲新啲既黎到著(都係舊，但舊之中新啲既🤣）突然覺得其實外婆可能比自己想像中更有心理準備，無論喺邊，可能對佢黎講，只要一家人喺一齊，佢就係幸福既。祝大家一家人平平安安、移英順利！"},{"pid":"75da1ea5d11f30fd954a0155f06073fe2d6fbc5a","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"八十歲都走<br />\n<br />\n連登仔仲有咩藉口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab43bb85b59bf6fbd691b87fdc99d7365eee028","tid":2409586,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"te]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38PEML3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38PEML3.png&h=612a24d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsAgOZp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsAgOZp.png&h=30b9f714&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"ba012b318325f0e841ff371df3d07e0e755e9819","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"一家人一條心<br />\n<br />\n真。齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053059f7de13746274f296170503926eaceb5897","tid":2409586,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"個婆婆香港出世？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04944d6a7eb5b68a785d84e9a5cad898a9a45caa","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aab43bb85b59bf6fbd691b87fdc99d7365eee028","tid":2409586,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"te]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38PEML3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38PEML3.png&h=612a24d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsAgOZp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsAgOZp.png&h=30b9f714&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"連登唔傾得BNO?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c249a33c2cb715c2f595274a30dc29c99e866e7","tid":2409586,"u