好珍惜。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"好多唐人醫生"},{"pid":"5ede9ae02dd83b9e14522ea455884b974a3f37ee","tid":2409586,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955b8ad5f82c4a47aa729794b63acced336f59b0","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1qQgYw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1qQgYw.png&h=6085b795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/599116127417126/posts/731533987508672/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F599116127417126%2Fposts%2F731533987508672%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=09d1bcdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/599116127417126/posts/731533987508672/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n外婆要移民<br />\n<br />\n小時候係外公外婆湊大的，特別有感情，外公十幾年前不在了，外婆到現在都同我父母同住。過去半年講到移民，都會諗咁外婆點呢？外婆雖然差不多80歲，但身體幾好，好有中氣，仲可以過年整24底年糕。英國近幾年也去過好幾次，倫敦同愛丁堡都去過，因為有家人喺度住。<br />\n<br />\n外婆喜歡英國的花園，夏天時會種下花。不喜歡英國的食物，有得揀一定要食中餐。覺得洗碗機都係信唔過，堅持手洗。<br />\n<br />\n每年夏天黎英國一兩個月的外婆，到底可唔可以真係喺度住呢？無得日日飲茶又真係得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n我們呢個extended family 有傾過，最後結果係因為所有子女都會走，所以外婆好有機會會跟隨。但係，移民咁大件事，每個家庭成員都應該有say, 每個人既睇法同感受都係重要既。問外婆既話，佢係答「你走我就走」(you jump I jump啲friend)。<br />\n<br />\n答就係答咗，但我心裏面仲有啲不安，會諗好多，其實會唔會係我地走，佢根本無得揀？就好似有得揀只想食中餐？有得揀都會想子女都喺香港？<br />\n<br />\n但<span class=\"red\">人生有幾多時係真正有得揀？</span><br />\n<br />\n有時候都會諗太祖父母當年可以揀<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>留喺廣州，可以揀落香港</strong></span></span>，揀咗香港，又有咗一代一代，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">當年佢地落既決定，影響以後既好多人</span></strong></span>。外婆依家80歲，還可以跟著我們再走一走，其實可能都幾大意義。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日同外婆視訊拜年，佢話最近買咗對新波鞋，打算黎英國著😂 牀下底啲舊衫都唔要啦，帶啲新啲既黎到著(都係舊，但舊之中新啲既🤣）突然覺得其實外婆可能比自己想像中更有心理準備，無論喺邊，可能對佢黎講，只要一家人喺一齊，佢就係幸福既。祝大家一家人平平安安、移英順利！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"移咗民就叫唐餐唔好再叫中餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f3ec2874218a9c9eec55b3d3e28dd160b5fe7b","tid":2409586,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"153cd9d27cfd76c70e7e76e624f1b8b6abacf184","tid":2409586,"uid":23194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"053059f7de13746274f296170503926eaceb5897","tid":2409586,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"個婆婆香港出世？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"唔係香港出世都可以歸化英藉<br />\n好多人都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e3f2a712e0ced1797d08f8ea52b0a275177d24","tid":2409586,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75da1ea5d11f30fd954a0155f06073fe2d6fbc5a","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"八十歲都走<br />\n<br />\n連登仔仲有咩藉口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"無錢走乜撚姐"},{"pid":"482c35df25f1b5bed76d052673dc74df11bccc7a","tid":2409586,"uid":25059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75da1ea5d11f30fd954a0155f06073fe2d6fbc5a","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"八十歲都走<br />\n<br />\n連登仔仲有咩藉口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"老西都走"},{"pid":"9b48be165ff6f1741b6aa9e22ca415f698657d17","tid":2409586,"uid":345353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75da1ea5d11f30fd954a0155f06073fe2d6fbc5a","tid":2409586,"uid":361751,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"八十歲都走<br />\n<br />\n連登仔仲有咩藉口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji